rue,"lemma_key":"أَصَرَّ","root":"أصر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n861","n862","n863",""],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to persist"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to insist","examples":[{"text":"لقد كان لديه حقيبة جميلة وأصَرّ أنْ يُقدِّمَهُ لي كَهدية.","english":"He had a beautiful bag and insisted on giving it to me as a gift."},{"text":"ويُصِرُّ العَالِم أيضًا أن الإسلام يدعو المؤمنين إلى الرحمة بالآخرين.","english":"The scholar also insists that Islam calls on believers to be merciful to others."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to resolve"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n861","headword_ar":"اَصْرٌ","root":"ASr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSorN","text_ar":"اـِصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; each in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n862","headword_ar":"اُصْرٌ","root":"ASr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSorN","text_ar":"اـِصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; each in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n863","headword_ar":"اـِصْرٌ","root":"ASr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A covenant, compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contract;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSorN","text_ar":"اُصْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSorN","text_ar":"اَصْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wSorN","text_ar":"وصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any bond arising from relationship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a covenant"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compact"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Is-hák,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from an oath:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a covenant, compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contract, which one does not fulfil, and for the neglecting and breaking of which one is punished:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the Kur ii. 286: (I' Ab:) [see also what follows, in two places:] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a heavy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burdensome, covenant, compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contract:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the Kur iii. 75: (ISh, M:) so, too, in the same vii. 156: (T, M:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=SaArN","text_ar":"ا=صَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a pl. of pauc.: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a heavy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burdensome, command;"},{"kind":"text","text":"such as was given to the Children of Israel to slay one another: so in the Kur ii. 286, accord. to Zj. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A weight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSorN","text_ar":"اُصْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSorN","text_ar":"اَصْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) so called because it restrains one from motion: (TA:) pl. as above. (M.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sin; a crime; an offence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSorN","text_ar":"اُصْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSorN","text_ar":"اَصْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) so called because of its weight, or burdensomeness: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sin of breaking a compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covenant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Sh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a grievous punishment of a sin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so accord. to AM in the Kur ii. 286. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that inclines one to a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=SirapN","text_ar":"ا=صِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". It is said in the Ham (p. 321) that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awaASiru","text_ar":"اَوَاصِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of the former word: but it is evidently pl. of the latter.] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A swearing by an oath which obliges one to divorce"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emancipate"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to pay a vow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) So in a trad., in which it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano Halafa EalaY yamiynK A_iSorN falaA kaf~aArapa lahaA","text_ar":"مَنْ حَلَفَ عَلَى يَمِينٍ اـِصْرٌ فَلَا كَفَّارَةَ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whoso sweareth an oath in which is an obligation to divorce"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emancipate"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to pay a vow, for it there is no expiation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: for such is the heaviest of oaths, and that from which the way of escape, or evasion, is most strait: the original meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASr","text_ar":"اصر"},{"kind":"text","text":"being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a burden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a binding."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ear-hole:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=SaArN","text_ar":"ا=صَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSoraAnN","text_ar":"اـِصْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","ISh","M","T","TA","Fr","Sh","IAar"]}]}}